\par Agency shall bill advertiser every 30 days and all bills shall be due and payable by advertiser within 10 days from the date of receipt with interest at the highest legal rate due thereafter. 
\par }\pard\plain \s3\qj \li0\ri0\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f1\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs22 DISCOUNTS 
