\par On termination of this contract by eith
er party, advertiser shall pay agency the cost of the material finished or in preparation, which advertiser has previously approved. Agency shall also be entitled to receive full commissions on any advertising that it has prepared and is eventually used b
y the advertiser. When all the agency\rquote s invoices are paid, agency shall deliver to advertiser all materials in its possession that were paid for by the advertiser. Advertiser shall assume Agency\rquote 
s responsibility for all outstanding contracts made on the advertiser\rquote s behalf. 
\par }\pard\plain \s3\qj \li0\ri0\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\faauto\outlinelevel2\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f1\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs22 NON-DISCLOSURE 
